:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253ceb1fee3609716cd8a434d432c6f3193f4822","tid":1268774,"uid":82121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:38:21.000Z","msg":"推，今晚返去就做野"},{"pid":"69ef0054816118fa94c64ef77dd39f3887fa8560","tid":1268774,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a849f9d35f5cd35ac6150daefc5ce4692178c3b","tid":1268774,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>報捷</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔係原本開post HKismyhome絲，但真係好想分享呢個好消息鼓勵下大家<br />\n有傳3間公司已撤TVB廣告，Expedia, <a href=\"http://hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhotels.com&d=ZcVshzlQZ77dxUPC5JM1BKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=372ac7ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hotels.com</a>, HKTV mall (hktv 7月頭完約後)，trivago廣告亦減咗<br />\n改變社會權力結構、文化及生態從來不易，但大家唔好低估鍵盤嘅力量，持之而恆落力轟炸就會有成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>預告：HKismyhome絲可能喺7月2日開始第二波</strong><br />\n<br />\n傳聞來自做marketing嘅朋友喺連登嘅回覆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/izCwoiX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/izCwoiX</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/izCwoQX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/izCwoQX</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dbmwBT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dbmwBT</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/izCwrLX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/izCwrLX</a><br />\n佢哋當然無可能喺公司網頁大大聲咁表明撤廣告啦，如果被迫睇TVB可自行fact check~<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">請大家去Facebok page瘋狂轟炸</span></span></strong><br />\n1. Trivago: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/trivagoHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FtrivagoHK&d=ZcVshzlQZ77dxUPC5JM1BKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=e5265b8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/trivagoHK</a><br />\n2. 幸福傷風素：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Fortune.Pharmacal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFortune.Pharmacal&d=ZcVshzlQZ77dxUPC5JM1BKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=1dfbd32d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Fortune.Pharmacal</a><br />\n<br />\n呢啲公司燒好多錢去做social media marketing，亦都好介意網民意見，大家咁樣洗版一定有用！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請瘋狂俾嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請瘋狂FB留言</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Trivago:</span><br />\n當世道無憂時我地想去旅行會諗起Trivago，希望宜家水深火熱之時Trivago會支持我地。<br />\n無綫新聞，助紂為虐<br />\n恥與為伍，撤回廣告<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">幸福傷風素：</span><br />\n香港病了，你能令佢好番嗎？我相信你可以的<br />\n無綫新聞，助紂為虐<br />\n恥與為伍，撤回廣告"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:39:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b1ccdb9f30b44d347fa222da69fe735568cb4587","tid":1268774,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"533a0ffe68d6f563d28b94154759def064e06cb0","tid":1268774,"uid":102700,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T04:45:01.000Z","msg":"Foodpanda係tvb狂賣廣告<br />\n連登仔識做啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:40:14.000Z","msg":"最近好似做緊優惠大把連登仔仆住用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3eabcda85e7c3e245974db18ac7cdd5af75410","tid":1268774,"uid":103014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:49:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"040c288d4bf6f580f985607db9bea7550fa8b5cb","tid":1268774,"uid":269967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:51:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2c364011f69f395552beb08663a9dc48b46a473f","tid":1268774,"uid":267969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"s